The following four logos were created and donated by
[Mihai Dragan](mailto:mihai.dragan@caatoosee.ro),
a [software developer](http://www.caatoosee.ro/)
who joined the Allegro community not very long ago, and wanted to give back
something in exchange for the excellent library. The logos were made with
[Gimp] and you are free to use and distribute them. In fact, if you want them
with other dimensions, colors or texts, just email him personally, since he has
the sources and can redraw them according to your suggestions.  Each logo is
sized 500x256 and weighs around 60KB. Click on the thumbnails to view the full
version.

